    "participants": "participants",
    "annualEdition": "annual edition",
    "title": "The biggest student",
    "titleHighlight": "hackathon in Central Asia",
    "para1": "HackNU is a 24-hour hackathon organized by the ACM Student Chapter at Nazarbayev University. Since its inception, HackNU has grown into one of the largest student hackathons in Central Asia, attracting participants from across the region.",
    "para2": "Whether you're a novice programmer or an experienced developer, HackNU provides the perfect environment to build innovative solutions, learn new technologies, and connect with like-minded individuals. Teams of 2-4 compete to create the best projects in various tracks.",
